data.description:
Life is better at  the lake!  This 2 bedroom/2.5 bath townhome is ready for move in! And investors, just so you know, there is no rental cap.   Caldwell Station welcomes you in the picturesque town of Cornelius.  This townhome features an open floor plan.  Two spacious master suites upstairs, each with private full baths and walk in closets.   This unit has a view of  the playground.  Other amenities beside the playground, are the park, clubhouse, fitness center and pool.  There is on street parking too!
You are minutes away from Birkdale Village, Caldwell Station Greenway and other lake amenities.   The community is located along Hwy 115 between exit 25 and 27 off of I 77.  Come see! Minimum 6 month lease and no rental cap.
